    <h1 style="color: #4CAF50;">Welcome to Spendique, <%= @user.username %>! 🎉</h1>
    <p>Hi there,</p>
    <p>First off, let’s address the elephant in the room: managing finances isn’t exactly what most people call “fun.” But here at <strong>Spendique</strong>, we’re on a mission to change that. We believe tracking your spending and improving your earning habits doesn’t have to feel like a chore—it can actually be rewarding (and maybe even fun).</p>
    <p>Here’s why we’re excited you joined us:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>You can now track every coin you spend and figure out where it went (yes, even that “mysterious” charge for snacks).</li>
      <li>Our tools give you insights into your earning and spending habits—think of us as your financial therapist.</li>
      <li>You’re part of a community that’s taking control of their money, one smart decision at a time.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>So, what’s next?</strong></p>
    <p>Activate your account below and get started:</p>
