    <p>I’m Steve, the founder and CEO of Spendique. When I’m not brainstorming ways to make money management easier for you, you’ll probably find me drinking too much coffee, obsessing over tech trends, or trying to beat my own savings goals (spoiler: Spendique helps me too!).</p>
